Â Â  Making the European Union the most competitive knowledge-based economy by 2010 involves two priorities, as far as I can see: investing heavily in Research and Development and removing the constraints weighing on businesses, and particularly on the smallest ones.
Despite the improved agreement obtained by the European Parliament, the European budget will not permit these huge investments to be made.
