It is crucial to involve the private sector in this effort, since we can clearly see that public budgets are not enough.
We therefore need to make progress with taxation in order to encourage businesses to invest more readily in R[amp]D.
This purposeful policy is what we are awaiting from the revised Lisbon Strategy, which needs to offer a stimulating, effective and, above all, simplified European regulatory framework for European businesses.
